Question : 
How can I programmatically tab to next control ? 

Answer : 
procedure TForm1.Edit1KeyPress(Sender: TObject; var Key: Char); 
begin 
  if Key = #32 then 
  begin 
    Key := #0; 
    PostMessage(Screen.ActiveForm.Handle, WM_NEXTDLGCTL, 0, 0); 
  end; 
end; 
  
  
  
  
